# 🚀 ElectroLaunch

A lightning-fast application launcher built with **Electron**, designed to streamline your workflow by providing instant access to applications, files, and websites through an elegant and minimalist interface.

![ElectroLaunch Banner](image/image.png)

## ✨ Key Features

- ⚡ **Instant Search & Launch** - Find and start any application in milliseconds with intelligent fuzzy search
- 🔗 **Smart Shortcuts** - Create custom shortcuts to applications, files, folders, and URLs with ease
- 🗑️ **Simple Management** - Add, edit, or remove shortcuts through an intuitive interface
- 📊 **Usage Analytics** - See which applications you use most frequently (privacy-focused, all data stored locally)
- 🎨 **Customizable Themes** - Choose between light, dark, and system modes for perfect visual comfort
- ⌨️ **Keyboard Navigation** - Control everything without touching your mouse for maximum productivity
- 🔄 **Automatic Updates** - Always enjoy the latest features and improvements

## 📥 Installation

### Pre-built Binaries

Download the latest version for your platform:

- [Windows (64-bit)](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/ElectroLaunch-Setup-Windows-x64.exe)
- [macOS](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/ElectroLaunch-darwin-x64.dmg)
- [Linux (.deb)](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/electro-launch_amd64.deb)
- [Linux (.AppImage)](https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch/releases/latest/download/ElectroLaunch-linux-x86_64.AppImage)

### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/fathuur7/electro-launch.git

# Navigate to project directory
cd electro-launch

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the application in development mode
npm start
```

### 📂 Folder Structure

```
.
├── main.js         # Main Electron process
├── preload.js      # (Opsional) Preload script
├── index.html      # HTML UI
├── renderer.js    # Logic untuk UI
├── src
│   ├── styles/     # CSS styles
└── package.json
```

---

## 🛠️ Building from Source

```bash
# For Windows
npm run build:win

# For macOS
npm run build:mac

# For Linux
npm run build:linux

# For all platforms
npm run build
```

## 🧩 Technology Stack

- **[Electron](https://www.electronjs.org/)** - Cross-platform desktop app framework
- **[Electron Forge](https://www.electronforge.io/)** - Complete toolchain for Electron app development
- **Core Node.js Modules:**
  - `fs` - File system operations
  - `path` - Path manipulations
  - `child_process` - Process execution
  - `os` - Operating system utilities

